Hunterpedia!

00:23:02.700 --> 00:23:03.470
It's Gon

00:23:03.470 --> 00:23:04.350
and Killua's

00:23:04.350 --> 00:23:06.030
Hunterpedia!

00:23:06.030 --> 00:23:08.300
Today, we introduce Zushi!

